rows.label: bf09120100_0020
rows.name:
I'm fine. More importantly, issue an evacuation 
advisory to the entire imperial capital.

rows.label: bf09120100_0030
rows.name:
You may use all military ships,
including my personal ones.

rows.label: bf09120100_0040
rows.name: Evacuate as many people as possible!

rows.label: bf09120100_0060
rows.name:
Never mind about me.
Hurry up!

rows.label: bf09120100_0070
rows.name: I'm afraid Superbia cannot hold out any longer.

rows.label: bf09120100_0110
rows.name:
[System:Ruby rt=Nee-san ]Cousin[/System:Ruby][ML:Dash ]
If you are there, I beg of you...

rows.label: bf09120100_0120
rows.name: Save Superbia, save this world's future...
